a\u357\'65, ke\u271\'0f v kone\u269\'0dnom d\u244\'f4sledku \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tny rozpo\u269\'0det na tom neuspor\u237\'ed a v podstate budeme len n\u250\'fati\u357\'65 be\u382\'7en\u253\'fdch sporite\u318\'3eov, aby vkladali viac pe\u328\'48az\u237\'ed do stavebn\u253\'fdch sporite\u318\'3en\u237\'ed, pri\u269\'0dom t\u237\'ed bud\u250\'fa na tom viac-menej profitova\u357\'65 v tomto smere. }
